messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图识别准确分类用户需求为营销规划相关意图",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
        "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别分类模块（可能是 LLM 调用或规则）未能正确将关于NBEV目标补全、增加理财师或优化产品方案的用户输入映射到营销规划意图，而是归类为“其他意图”，导致后续流程路由到 non_agent 阶段。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "intent": "4001",
          "source": "run_trace.raw_response"
        },
        {
          "intent_name": "其他意图",
          "source": "run_trace.raw_response"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "系统路由至正确阶段避免过早结束",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py (stage assignment)",
        "app/workflow/steps/path_dispatch.py (routing logic)"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于上游 intent_recognition 错误地输出了“其他意图”，路径分派阶段据此将请求路由到 non_agent 阶段，导致系统过早结束，未能进入澄清或规划步骤。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "stage": "non_agent",
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "契约期望 stage 为 intent，但实际输出 non_agent，根因同样源于 intent_recognition 的错误分类。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "expected_stage": "intent",
          "actual_stage": "non_agent"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
    "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py",
    "app/schemas/intent.py",
    "app/workflow/steps/path_dispatch.py"
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块(intent_recognition)未能将包含业务指标(NBEV)和具体行动方案(增加理财师/优化产品方案)的用户请求识别为营销规划相关意图，而是错误分类为“其他意图”(intent:4001)，导致流程被派往 non_agent 阶段并立即终止，未能进入后续规划链路。可能原因包括意图分类模型训练数据不足、prompt 设计未涵盖此类长尾意图，或意图映射规则不完整。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "key": "intent",
      "value": "4001",
      "source": "raw_response"
    },
    {
      "key": "intent_name",
      "value": "其他意图",
      "source": "raw_response"
    },
    {
      "key": "stage",
      "value": "non_agent",
      "source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage"
    },
    {
      "key": "planning_output_probe.stage_match",
      "value": false
    },
    {
      "key": "judge_result.fulfillment_assessments",
      "value": "意图识别准确分类用户需求 not_fulfilled"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

